<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 09:13:01 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>保时捷与 ClearMotion 合作提供平稳的悬架技术</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/porsche-partners-with-clearmotion-its-smooth-suspension-tech-2024-04-09/</link><description>两家公司周二表示，德国豪华汽车制造商保时捷已与 ClearMotion 合作，验证这家美国初创公司的主动悬架技术和路读软件，并签署了技术许可协议。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 09:03:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/porsche-partners-with-clearmotion-its-smooth-suspension-tech-2024-04-09/</guid></item><item><title>金管局首席执行官表示，香港正在考虑“深化”与中国的一些联系计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/hkma-ceo-says-hong-kong-considering-deepening-some-connect-schemes-with-china-2024-04-09/</link><description>香港金融管理局（金管局）首席执行官余伟文周二表示，正在考虑深化香港与中国大陆之间的一些投资联系计划。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 08:58:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/hkma-ceo-says-hong-kong-considering-deepening-some-connect-schemes-with-china-2024-04-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国第一季度电动汽车销量增速创一年新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-car-sales-rise-57-yy-march-2024-04-09/</link><description>周二的行业数据显示，随着以本土宠儿比亚迪为首的汽车制造商加大折扣力度并提供融资工具以促进销量，中国 3 月份电动乘用车销量同比增长 10.5%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 08:16:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-car-sales-rise-57-yy-march-2024-04-09/</guid></item><item><title>中共中央政治局委员赵立坚率代表团访问朝鲜</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-communist-party-politburo-member-zhao-lead-delegation-north-korea-kcna-2024-04-09/</link><description>据朝鲜官方通讯社朝中社周二报道，由最高立法委员、党的三号官员赵乐际率领的中国政府和共产党代表团将对朝鲜进行正式友好访问。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 07:20:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-communist-party-politburo-member-zhao-lead-delegation-north-korea-kcna-2024-04-09/</guid></item><item><title>据彭博社报道，中国工商银行计划出售 55 亿美元的损失吸收债券</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinas-icbc-plans-55-bln-sale-loss-absorbing-bonds-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-04-09/</link><description>据彭博社周二报道，中国工商银行计划最快本月发行高达 400 亿元人民币（55 亿美元）的总损失吸收能力（TLAC）债券。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 06:57:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinas-icbc-plans-55-bln-sale-loss-absorbing-bonds-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-04-09/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾抗议者践踏习近平肖像，谴责中国海上“侵略”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-protesters-trample-xi-effigy-condemn-chinas-maritime-aggression-2024-04-09/</link><description>周二，马尼拉的抗议者践踏中国国家主席习近平的肖像，谴责中国在南海“侵略”菲律宾。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 06:23:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-protesters-trample-xi-effigy-condemn-chinas-maritime-aggression-2024-04-09/</guid></item><item><title>台湾军演模拟击退中国演习演变成攻击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-war-games-simulate-repelling-chinese-drill-that-turns-into-attack-2024-04-09/</link><description>台湾国防部周二表示，今年台湾的年度军演将在海上进行“杀伤区”演习，以打破封锁，并模拟中国突然将其环岛常规演习转变为实际攻击的场景。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 05:14:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-war-games-simulate-repelling-chinese-drill-that-turns-into-attack-2024-04-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国的不确定性给奢侈品行业的前景蒙上阴影</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-uncertainty-clouds-outlook-luxury-sector-2024-04-09/</link><description>当奢侈品公司公布第一季度业绩时，投资者正准备迎接奢侈品销售大幅放缓的局面，这反映出中国需求低迷，以及与去年中国大陆解除新冠限制措施提振销售时的情况相比。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 04:04:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-uncertainty-clouds-outlook-luxury-sector-2024-04-09/</guid></item><item><title>拉夫罗夫表示，俄罗斯和中国将讨论在欧亚大陆深化安全合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-china-cooperate-fight-against-terrorism-russian-agencies-cite-lavrov-2024-04-09/</link><description>俄罗斯外交部长谢尔盖·拉夫罗夫周二在北京会谈后表示，俄罗斯和中国已同意讨论如何深化欧洲和亚洲的安全合作，以对抗美国将其意志强加于该地区的企图。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 03:01:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-china-cooperate-fight-against-terrorism-russian-agencies-cite-lavrov-2024-04-09/</guid></item><item><title>据彭博社报道，瑞银考虑与北京政府进行瑞信中国股权互换</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/ubs-weighs-credit-suisse-china-stake-swap-with-beijing-government-bloomberg-news-2024-04-09/</link><description>据彭博社周一报道，瑞银正在洽谈通过将其在瑞士信贷旗下境内证券公司的股份与北京政府投资基金进行互换，获得其中国平台的全部所有权。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 00:54:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/ubs-weighs-credit-suisse-china-stake-swap-with-beijing-government-bloomberg-news-2024-04-09/</guid></item><item><title>参议院共和党领袖支持立法迫使中国撤资 TikTok</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/senate-republican-leader-backs-legislation-force-chinese-divestment-tiktok-2024-04-08/</link><description>美国参议院共和党领袖米奇·麦康奈尔周一呼吁立法，迫使 TikTok 的母公司中国字节跳动剥离 1.7 亿美国人使用的短视频应用程序。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 21:41:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/senate-republican-leader-backs-legislation-force-chinese-divestment-tiktok-2024-04-08/</guid></item><item><title>调查获悉，加拿大间谍发现中国干预了最近两次选举</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/canada-spies-found-china-interfered-last-two-elections-probe-hears-2024-04-08/</link><description>加拿大国内间谍机构周一听取了一项官方调查，得出结论认为中国干预了最近两次选举，这是迄今为止涉嫌中国干预加拿大政治的最确凿证据。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 21:09:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/canada-spies-found-china-interfered-last-two-elections-probe-hears-2024-04-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国部长表示干邑白兰地调查与欧盟对电动汽车的调查无关 - 消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-minister-says-probe-cognac-not-linked-eu-probe-electric-vehicles-2024-04-08/</link><description>法国商务部消息人士周一表示，中国商务部部长王文涛告诉法国财政部长布鲁诺·勒梅尔，中国针对干邑白兰地市场发起的调查与欧盟针对中国电动汽车发起的调查无关。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 19:34:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-minister-says-probe-cognac-not-linked-eu-probe-electric-vehicles-2024-04-08/</guid></item><item><title>IDC称全球个人电脑市场在经历两年下滑后第一季度恢复增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/global-pc-market-returns-growth-first-quarter-after-two-year-decline-idc-says-2024-04-08/</link><description>市场研究公司国际数据公司（IDC）周一发布的初步结果显示，全球个人电脑出货量在经历两年下滑后，第一季度恢复增长。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 18:30:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/global-pc-market-returns-growth-first-quarter-after-two-year-decline-idc-says-2024-04-08/</guid></item><item><title>英国称 AUKUS 与其他国家的合作谈判将于今年开始</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/collaboration-talks-between-aukus-other-nations-begin-this-year-uk-says-2024-04-08/</link><description>英国周一表示，其 AUKUS 安全条约伙伴、美国和澳大利亚以及包括日本在内的其他国家之间的未来合作磋商将于今年开始。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 15:48:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/collaboration-talks-between-aukus-other-nations-begin-this-year-uk-says-2024-04-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>